{"type": "article", "id": 26473, "title": "棱角分明的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-06T07:07:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162019ODsR46vC0eGcdTuU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">还记得小时候玩过的折纸游戏吗？<a href=\"http://odesd2.com/\">ODESD2</a> 设计的这款名为 <a href=\"http://odesd2.com/en/furniture/chairs/q5_chair\">Q5</a> 的椅子棱角分明，看上去像是一个被放大的折纸作品。实际上由铝合金制成的 Q5 不仅坚固也非常轻便，底座还有多种颜色可选。不仅如此，它座位上的毛毡也可以定制。售价为 326 欧元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162017UsjgAE18GhqaDcux.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162017AQ7MlYeXxcIEnb3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162018WAEu6XkOrCzv8DRs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162018i8E3ymrHpAMP02Zk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}